TEST CASE 1: AUTH SERVICE - SIGNUP PATH TESTING
Objective: Test all independent paths in signup() method (M=5)
Type: Basis Path Testing with Cyclomatic Complexity M=5

Basis Path Coverage:

  [Path 1 - Invalid Email Format]
  Precondition: Invalid email input
  Input: email="invalid-email"
  Decision Points: Email validation → FAIL
  Assertion: ValidationException thrown
  Expected: Email format validation error

  [Path 2 - Duplicate Email]
  Precondition: Email exists in database
  Input: email="existing@test.com"
  Decision Points: Email validation → PASS, Uniqueness check → FAIL
  Assertion: ConflictException thrown
  Expected: Duplicate email error

  [Path 3 - Weak Password]
  Precondition: Valid email, weak password
  Input: password="weak"
  Decision Points: Email validation → PASS, Uniqueness → PASS, Password strength → FAIL
  Assertion: ValidationException thrown
  Expected: Password weakness error

  [Path 4 - Creation Failure]
  Precondition: Valid inputs but DB error
  Input: Valid email, strong password
  Decision Points: All validations → PASS, Creation → FAIL
  Assertion: Error handling → Rollback
  Expected: Database error logged

  [Path 5 - Successful Signup]
  Precondition: All preconditions met
  Input: Valid email, strong password, unique
  Decision Points: All validations → PASS, Creation → SUCCESS
  Assertion: User created with hashed password
  Expected: User object returned with token

Cyclomatic Complexity: M = 5
Coverage Achieved: 100% of basis paths
Decision Coverage: 100%

TEST CASE 2: ORDER SERVICE - CREATEORDER PATH TESTING
Objective: Test all independent paths in createOrder() (M=7)
Type: Basis Path Testing with Cyclomatic Complexity M=7

Basis Path Coverage:

  [Path 1 - User Not Authenticated]
  Decision Points: Auth check → FAIL
  Input: No/invalid token
  Assertion: 401 Unauthorized
  Expected: Auth failure

  [Path 2 - Empty Cart]
  Decision Points: Auth → PASS, Cart validation → FAIL
  Input: Empty cart ID
  Assertion: 400 Bad Request
  Expected: Cart validation error

  [Path 3 - Stock Unavailable]
  Decision Points: Auth → PASS, Cart → PASS, Stock check → FAIL
  Input: Requested qty > available
  Assertion: 409 Conflict
  Expected: Stock reservation failed

  [Path 4 - Invalid Coupon]
  Decision Points: Auth → PASS, Cart → PASS, Stock → PASS, Coupon → INVALID
  Input: Invalid coupon code
  Assertion: Order proceeds without discount
  Expected: Coupon skipped, no error

  [Path 5 - Payment Failure]
  Decision Points: Auth → PASS, Cart → PASS, Stock → PASS, Coupon → OK, Payment → FAIL
  Input: Card declined
  Assertion: Rollback all inventory reservations
  Expected: Order creation aborted, inventory freed

  [Path 6 - Notification Failure]
  Decision Points: Auth → PASS, Cart → PASS, Stock → PASS, Coupon → OK, Payment → OK, Notification → FAIL
  Input: Email service down
  Assertion: Continue with retry queue
  Expected: Order created, notification retried

  [Path 7 - Complete Success]
  Decision Points: All checks → PASS
  Input: Valid user, cart, payment, coupon, notification success
  Assertion: Order confirmed with ID
  Expected: Order created with status PENDING

Cyclomatic Complexity: M = 7
Coverage Achieved: 100% of basis paths
Decision Coverage: 100%

